    <h1>Klon Centaur</h1>
    <div class="meta">January 09, 2026 · Fuzz</div>

    <p>This is another circuit that made it's way to my pedal board, but has since been removed. Nothing wrong with the circuit, just not my cup of tea.<br>
The circuit I built sounded a little muffled, could be the clippers I used or the op amps, I don't know. Maybe that's how they sound.<br>
I used NOS Russian D9D diodes for clippers, TL072 op amps for both IC's (did have an NE5532 for the 2nd one for a bit) <br>
and changed the tone pot to B20K to give it a little more brightness at the top of the range.<br><br>
